response.overview: In a gritty, resilient community, rapper Lolo Vandal uses music to inspire and protect youth, while secretly building a future empire of justice and creativity. Season 1 follows his battle to balance fatherhood, leadership, and covert missions as he faces threats that challenge his vision and loyalty.
